{"tid":1761820,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"強敵已去 李嘉欣有得贏","createTime":"2019-11-29T07:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T07:51:09.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27a811de51f4a0708353cf7003591f5b6bcf2e3c","tid":1761820,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:07:52.000Z","msg":"何澤堯近期頭馬接踵而來，現時已有13場頭馬在手。正所謂人紅自然多馬揀，而且大部分時候都選擇正確，剛周三（20日）揀「肥仔威威」而捨「管之星」正是一例。<br />\n<br />\n周末（23日）第四場四班1600米草地，何澤堯有「陽光」及「福多寶」可揀，不過仍選擇再為摩廐馬「七寶」效力，觀乎此駒近仗表現，相信騎者今次無揀錯。<br />\n<br />\n「七寶」馬主為許晉亨及李嘉欣兩位城中名人，加上大摩和許氏家族淵源深厚，自然希望早點為此駒建功。奈何「七寶」比較遲熟，雖然至今已有六次上名，仍與頭馬緣慳一線。<br />\n<br />\n四歲馬始終會進步，剛戰在何澤堯發揮下表現甚佳，只負於大熱門「水箭龜」而力壓其他對手，今場已無超級馬在陣，「七寶」如能順風順水，應可如願勝回一仗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vekMwLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvekMwLz.jpg&h=01705a22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd615db04ac34989fec55027e125791ff81f49f1","tid":1761820,"uid":59920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"睇錯何君堯近期頭馬接踵而來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996195fda1f66d53bced0de8f89754e17a149ece","tid":1761820,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"你同小美想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0199d06761d8a5266ba687f4ab0bfde740ae9953","tid":1761820,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"996195fda1f66d53bced0de8f89754e17a149ece","tid":1761820,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"你同小美想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vp1csyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvp1csyd.png&h=d31f57b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5e42cceaf80a4ce53d08bbb6c71e6a1d9872a11","tid":1761820,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xhi7yk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xhi7yk.png&h=410a9029&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}